          stays confidential and is never logged.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong> - Enjoy a clean, intuitive layout
          for quick, hassle-free use.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Common Use Cases -->
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Common Use Cases</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-2">
        <li>
